Package: wombat
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: GTK4 and libadwaita desktop shell around Numbat
 Wombat is a desktop front-end for the Numbat language that keeps a live
 interpreter session in memory and shows the full output history in a
 scrollable log.